    <j.0:type rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Position de la Commission sur les amendements du PE en première lecture</j.0:type>
    <j.2:build_info>cdm:CDM_2.1.7  tdm:1523  xslt:3945 saxon:9.0.0.1J JVM:1.6.0_29 metaconvJar:1.1.9 builddate:13/02/2014 07:11:58</j.2:build_info>
    <j.0:comment xml:lang="en">Of the eighteen amendments adopted by the Parliament, the Commission accepts fifteen (1,2,4,5,6,7,8,9,10,12,13,14,15,16,17), of which two with redrafting (18,3). It refuses three, closely linked amendments (9,10,11)</j.0:comment>
    <j.0:has_type rdf:resource="http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/event/POS_AME_R1_byCOM"/>
    <j.0:event_legal_comment xml:lang="en">Of the eighteen amendments adopted by the Parliament, the Commission accepts fifteen (1,2,4,5,6,7,8,9,10,12,13,14,15,16,17), of which two with redrafting (18,3). It refuses three, closely linked amendments (9,10,11)</j.0:event_legal_comment>
